# OMC orchestration tool state (not part of the project)
.omc/

# Publisher signing material. `cmd/pluginsign` reads a raw 32-byte Ed25519 seed from a
# file path, so a stray `seed.bin` in the working tree is one `git add -A` away from
# being published. Never commit key material; keep seeds outside the repo.
*.key
*.pem
*.seed
seed
seed.*
*_seed
*.bin
